{"tid":2355703,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"十大爛尾作品","createTime":"2021-01-06T09:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T04:01:36.000Z","uid":199804,"like":10,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"88cf116fa28bf1a2e76e38760341573737f4f3f1","tid":2355703,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:24:27.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">10.我們真的乜乜乜</span></span><br />\n學撚埋古味啲濕鳩野，仲要分咁撚多支線結局，多鳩餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">9.五等分的乜乜</span></span><br />\n明明係嚟搞笑嘅弱智角色最後變撚左正女主角，全因以前有約定。就算其他四條女各方屌打曬佢都要夾硬揀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">8.偽戀</span></span><br />\n五等分的乜乜嘅相反，成套野講到個約定幾撚咁重要，結局就用一兩話講唔係約定之人都唔緊要，咁講黎比撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">7.約定的乜乜乜</span></span><br />\n結尾為止明明仲好刺激點知話走就走搞到人即刻無癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">6.妖尾</span></span><br />\n主角光環太撚離譜搞到後尾冇曬刺激感，反正每次斷手斷腳一句「我們是妖精尾巴」就即刻秒殺對面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">5.銀魂</span></span><br />\n喺呢個list上第二個可以接受嘅爛尾。畢竟套野主要都係日常，打boss只係支線。打boss其實喺日常入面夾雜嘅伏筆/鋪排都幾好，係最尾收尾太倉促。應該係唯一一套唔會因為爛尾而失去fans嘅漫畫<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">4. Magi</span></span><br />\n後尾成套野勁on9,最深刻係新八同xx喺度拍烏蠅互相拍拍拍勁弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">3. Bleach</span></span><br />\n呢個大家都明，到藍染應該一早完，雖然唔會做到咩神作但起碼成套野最終boss係開掛嘅藍染，唔係隻自稱上帝全知全能但比橙頭佬平A死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">2.七大罪</span></span><br />\n牙suck王一出場已經好多人諗會唔會最後反客為主佢會殺左團長。到最後先知原來堂堂亞瑟王只係一個配角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">1.鬼滅之刃</span></span><br />\n啱啱講過銀魂係第二可以接受嘅爛尾，鬼滅就係第一個。至於點解可以接受？因為冇期待就冇落差，就唔會達唔到讀者要求。而冇人會對垃圾有期待，完。"},{"pid":"97d38158c5f384295a5efa2bfa2ea2d794d39bed","tid":2355703,"uid":10612,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:29:34.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>成神之日阿你老母</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"12fb148fa99af05b21e7970ccb8ebaeab3a7abec","tid":2355703,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97d38158c5f384295a5efa2bfa2ea2d794d39bed","tid":2355703,"uid":10612,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:29:34.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>成神之日阿你老母</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:30:28.000Z","msg":"想講漫畫only,重開<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08912a178d09e71b5179aa6361487bfd010c672","tid":2355703,"uid":144064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:30:44.000Z","msg":"家教都冇<br />\n垃圾post"},{"pid":"a78517a17f59c09d0dd047a3dff6de9a5ca6d214","tid":2355703,"uid":522,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:31:49.000Z","msg":"<del>1.鬼滅之刃</del><br />\n<br />\n1. 粉俠傳"},{"pid":"21d5f26212b55c1595c8a2a9910def3bf94da881","tid":2355703,"uid":250291,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:31:51.000Z","msg":"【2021首個行動post】全民文宣連儂日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2355614/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2355614/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CJsjOhkFPlJ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJsjOhkFPlJ%2F&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=4767100f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2