D601A92AB&h=bc15e78d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎明未來到，先有大抓捕。<br />\n抗爭平靜片刻，港共立即反噬。<br />\n港共就係要我地恐懼。<br />\n要我地放棄。<br />\n要我地徒勞。<br />\n<br />\n唯獨抗爭意志不滅。<br />\n8/1-11/1，星光燎原，遍地開花！<br />\n寧鳴而死，不默而生！"},{"pid":"8b4cfd8b421ceed372c492307cc9f900d5a5812d","tid":2355703,"uid":185057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:32:53.000Z","msg":"7大罪最撚垃圾係明明打完佢老豆，<br />\n然後又再loop多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34dad0ae62202e96a47f9b7533024fe6e5143a40","tid":2355703,"uid":199804,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"21d5f26212b55c1595c8a2a9910def3bf94da881","tid":2355703,"uid":250291,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:31:51.000Z","msg":"【2021首個行動post】全民文宣連儂日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2355614/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2355614/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CJsjOhkFPlJ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJsjOhkFPlJ%2F&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=4767100f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJsjOhkFPlJ%2F&h=2eee38b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CJsjOhkFPlJ/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lhr8-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/135760301_2741317849516339_41508721484844777_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=a26aad&amp;_nc_ohc=WjLqJBXQcqUAX_tLILU&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-lhr8-2.xx&amp;oh=fb638f3c6308a3eb2b313b82b59d520b&amp;oe=601C7DDA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lhr8-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F135760301_2741317849516339_41508721484844777_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3Da26aad%26_nc_ohc%3DWjLqJBXQcqUAX_tLILU%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lhr8-2.xx%26oh%3Dfb638f3c6308a3eb2b313b82b59d520b%26oe%3D601C7DDA&h=3f6a81b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lhr8-